#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_alerts.rst:114
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Set Contract Health value` is selected in "
"the :guilabel:`Action To Do` field, the following field appears:"
msgstr ""
"Jeśli w polu :guilabel:`Akcja do wykonania` wybrano :guilabel:`Ustaw wartość "
