#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/scheduled_actions.rst:46
msgid ""
"Determine if a scheduled action is active by looking under "
"the :guilabel:`Active` column, in the it's corresponding row on "
"the :guilabel:`Scheduled Actions` dashboard, for a ticked checkbox; if the "
